{
  "stem": "1502.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As far as I remember, there was a-- a sense of community.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were many Jewish organizations that helped-- that helped other Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a strong sense of community.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I left Poland in 1930.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we moved to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father decided to move to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even so, we had visas for South Africa and for Belgium.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father decided to emigrate to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In-- in Belgium, in 19-- 1933, when Hitler came to power in Germany, things-- we-- we did feel that there's a certain-- there's a certain removed danger coming, like a dark cloud.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because Nazis were spreading all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in Belgium-- Belgium was a very liberal country, very democratic country, but a Nazi party was founded in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as Hitler grew in Germany, so did the Nazi parties in the other parts of Europe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were two Nazi parties in Belgium, because the Belgian people consist of two people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There's the Flemish people, who speak Flemish, and the French speaking people, which are called Walloons.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Nazi party of the French speaking people was-- was founded by a-- by a Belgium named Leon Degrelle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Flemish party had a different-- different person, which I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the main was the French speaking Nazi party, which at elections, I think, in 1937 or 1938, had 600,000 votes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they had a number, a quite substantial number of deputies in the parliament.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was called-- the party was called Rex, R-E-X.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was a-- it-- it was a direct branch of the Nazi Party from Germany, which later on, when the Germans came in, joined the Nazis and were considered by the Belgians as traitors.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
